---
title: Flank Steak & Garlic-Parmesan Mash with Balsamic Veggies & Herby Butter
description: Lean, rich and meaty - all perfect descriptive words for the humble flank steak! This flavourful cut of beef doesn’t need fancy sides - tonight, we’re having it with cheesy garlic mash and tangy balsamic veggies. A dollop of herb butter will melt into the steak, coating it in extra flavour and decadence. Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
